    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-01-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-01-15T11:00:00-05:00" n="61"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d61">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Chinese Republican Minister for Foreign
                            Affairs</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Nanking</hi>
                        </placeName> (<date
                            ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates"
                            calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1912-01-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                            notBefore="1912-01-16T00:00:00+08:00">undated</date>; received Jan. 17,
                        1912).</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Republican Government has been firmly established. To facilitate our intercourse
                    with foreign countries and enable us the better to fulfill our international
                    obligations, I earnestly urge upon you the advisability of recognizing our
                    Government at an early date.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wang Chung Hui</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
